{"tid":1033880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門一休班警涉藏毒　與同行涉販毒男女齊被捕","createTime":"2019-02-23T13:27:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T14:10:46.000Z","uid":79563,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"26b9491820c4c7cf1f76f049adc0cb0bab40a36c","tid":1033880,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T13:27:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190222/s00001/d72f73eab71a1f61e42893e777e0edc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190222%2Fs00001%2Fd72f73eab71a1f61e42893e777e0edc3.jpg&h=21005295&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方根據線報，昨午5時許，派員掩至屯門龍門路一大廈埋伏，其間3名目標男女出現。探員隨即上前截查，並在其中一名46歲陳姓男子身上，檢獲1.65克共值660元的懷疑氯胺酮。<br />\n<br />\n警方經調查，發現陳為休班警務人員，他涉嫌藏毒被捕。同行21歲蘇姓男子及20歲袁姓女子，亦涉嫌販毒被捕帶署。案件交由毒品調查科人員跟進。<br />\n<br />\n警方強調，非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"1a725f98a6f362a5febf1a1a207fdcec0a7bab89","tid":1033880,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T13:29:43.000Z","msg":"陰功，走粉都要做埋"},{"pid":"0da5708f8bff9fac3f6d30dc63c657a9d0817fac","tid":1033880,"uid":280,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T13:35:44.000Z","msg":"警察搞咩呀⋯⋯香港都已經俾支那搞到亂<br />\n係咪咁大壓力 不如唔好哂個位啦 俾我做啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3259b801fc2ab68ec86d98bbd2a7c917004515","tid":1033880,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T13:36:32.000Z","msg":"高層震怒未?"},{"pid":"d47daf861ef4ae27bd41f337d69cf045a5d3cc85","tid":1033880,"uid":31715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T13:52:40.000Z","msg":"休班警+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935fe37df0c2346241e471326b58a84a1da03d81","tid":1033880,"uid":22756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T13:52:55.000Z","msg":"呀蛇秘撈唔洗你教"},{"p